The paper discusses the cybersecurity of industrial control systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the shift of ICS from stand-alone systems to cloud-based environments, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the applicability of machine learning techniques for ICS cybersecurity, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cybersecurity (cs.CY).
